23:03.500 --> 23:10.380
If free will really is gone, let's say that it just turns out that undeniably, unrefutably,

23:10.380 --> 23:12.240
there is zero free will.

23:12.240 --> 23:17.500
Not all free will, not partial free will and partial uncontrollability.

23:17.500 --> 23:18.500
Zero free will.

